            We respect the intellectual property of others, and we ask our users to do the same. Accordingly, we
            observe and comply with the DMCA, and have adopted the following Notice and Takedown Policy relating
            to claims of copyright infringement by our customers, subscribers or users.
        </p>
        
        <h4>Take Down Procedure</h4>
